text: Carveth may refer to: * Carveth Read — was a 19th and 20th century British philosopher and logician. He was born 16 March 1848 in Falmouth, Cornwall, England. * Carveth Thompson — is an American former politician in the state of South Dakota. * Carveth Geach — served as the Chief Scout of the Boy Scouts of South Africa.
